@startuml Admin_Notifications

title Admin - Notifications (Module D)

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"

rectangle "NOTIFICATIONS" {
    usecase "View System\nNotifications" as D15
    usecase "Mark Notif\nAs Read" as D16
    usecase "Send System\nAnnouncement" as NM1
    usecase "View Notif\nLog History" as NM2
}

Admin --> D15: 1. View notifications
D15 --> D16: Mark as read
Admin --> NM1: 2. Send announcement
Admin --> NM2: 3. View log history

note right of D15
  **Priority:** P1 (Important)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
